Presentational Components:

* TrackingGroupList
  - groups: { id, text, trackers } shape
  - onGroupClick(id: number)

* Tracker
  - id: number
  - title: string
  - pendings: { unit, pending, base, goal } shape
  - categories: { id, amt }
  - onGoalClick(id: number)
  - onCounterClick(id: number)

* Pending
  wires up the TimePending with now from Redux
  - unit: string
  - pending: any
  - base: number
  - goal: number

* TimePending
  - now: Date
  - start: Date | null
  - base: number
  - goal: number

* TimeGoal
  - pending: number
  - base: number
  - goal: number
  - onClick()

* TimeCounter
  - pending: number
  - onClick()

Container Components:

Ticker
  - default offsetms = 0
  - takes firebase.database().ref('.info/serverTimeOffset').on('value', snap => { offsetms = snap.val() })
  - updates state.now to new Date(new Date().getTime() + offsetms)

UserTrackingGroupList
  - auth

VisiblePending
  - tracker: id
  - unit: string
  - onClick
